title: Gwyneth Paltrow 'Not' Sabotaging Chris Martin & New GF

og.title: Gwyneth Paltrow 'Not' Sabotaging Chris Martin & New GF - video dailymotion
og.description: Gwyneth Paltrow and Chris Martin are still friendly exes, despite a report. A recent story claimed Paltrow was trying to sabotage Martin’s relationship with Dakota Johnson because of their age difference. Martin is 41 and Johnson is 28.The article even insisted Gwyneth was changing up their children’s schedules so Chris would have to cancel plans with Dakota. It turns out, however, that none of it is true.Gossip Cop checked in with Paltrow’s spokesperson who called the report “ridiculous.”
